<p>Prices start at $365 USD per person and that includes everything except your drinks, gratuities, and the $22 USD Guna entrance fee which you&rsquo;ll have to pay upon entry to the region.&nbsp;You can <strong><a href="https://www.viator.com/tours/San-Blas-Islands/3-days-2-nights-in-San-Blas-with-trip-to-Cayos-Holandeses-Day-Tour/d4516-127626P54?pid=P00050132&amp;mcid=42383&amp;medium=link&amp;campaign=ttk-san-blas-islands" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener sponsored nofollow">book this 3-day tour online here</a></strong>. </p>



