<p>Not only this, but they&rsquo;re culturally rich and allow you to totally disconnect from the modern world. A trip to the San Blas Islands is an amazing adventure and a total must when visiting Panama. You won&rsquo;t regret it!&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>



